 Prepare;testPath;testFilename;ask;answer;options;flag;ind
‚çù Creates an instance of the class `Tester2` named `T` and configures it for
‚çù Assumes that the project is handled by the project manager "Cider", and that there is
‚çù a namespace ##.CiderConfig available with the Cider config parameters.
‚çù As a side effect is creates a folder "TestResults" in the project's root folder if the
‚çù user wants to do code coverage with the `CodeCoverage` class.
